			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">An Introduction:
<br />

<br />
Groff and I have worked on this from time to time when feeling especially introspective... and/or base.  Neither of us could think of anything particularly interesting to write about, so we chose to simply recount the exploits of two homeless Trolls.  This was originally a message board thread, which made it clear who wrote which pieces.  Given the extreme amount of laziness present in the authoring staff, it's now one big post.<br />_________________<br />65 Troll Shaman 
<br />
LFHC (Looking for Home City)
<br />
<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=602910>Who says you can't wear split paw armor in your 60's?</a>
<br />

<br />
Board Troll.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
