		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row1"><span class="name"><a name="15072"></a><b>Groff Gorespiller</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails"><br /><img src="http://www.grobbtrolls.us/trolls/images/trllhd.gif" alt="" border="0" /><br /><br />Joined: 03 Dec 2003<br />Posts: 297<br />Location: Cincinnati, OH</span><br /></td>
		<td class="row1" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
			<tr>
				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=15072&amp;sid=122ee81db202a676fba0b56b9a12c860#15072"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Mon Jan 12, 2004 3:12 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: </span></td>
				<td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=15072&amp;sid=122ee81db202a676fba0b56b9a12c860"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
